<div class="container">
  <div class="bloc2 mt-2">
    <h1>Presentation</h1>
    <p>Fresh alumni from LeWagon coding bootcamp - ready for my next challenge ! A travel enthusiast in love w/ code that enjoys being outdoors !</p>
